	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non est, quod scribam de tumultu illo bellico; nam a magistrato nostro id intelliges.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Video <placeName ref="place70">Augustam Vindelicorum</placeName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><placeName ref="place70">Augsburg</placeName>.</note> valde trepidare et forte propter amplissimas opes unam peti prae aliis urbibus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt, lantgravium<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Philipp von Hessen.</note> a militibus et equitibus nescio quibus detineri, quo minus possit Germanicis urbibus ferre suppetias.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego vero famae nihil credo.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero illum propediem affuturum iusto instructum exercitu.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Silent constanter fratres Inferioris Germaniae.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In diem expecto, quid sint de motibus suis scripturi.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Imo paucula adhuc <placeName ref="place97">Basilienses</placeName> ad magistratum nostrum dedere.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certum est, ducem Wirtenbergensem<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="person224">Ulrich von Württemberg</persName>.</note> forti et intrepido animo esse<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">s. Blarer an HB, 25. Juni.</note> et auxilia laturum fida urbibus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego ne de Helvetiis quidem despero.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sis in hoc, ut tui quoque Badenae fideles sint.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person1335">Dux</persName> Bavariae<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="person20760">Wilhelm IV.</persName> von Bayern.</note> respondisse dicitur caesari<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="person20184">Karl V.</persName></note>, nolle se armis propter religionem certare; ergo praetexit causas caesar alias.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nobiles Rheni negarunt auxilia caesari.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu si quae certiora habes, communica.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vive et vale!</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus dominum, ut animum et robur nostris inspiret, adversariis metum et vertiginem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">28. iunii anno 1546.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">H. Bullingerus tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. d[octori] <persName ref="person226">Ioachimo Vadiano</persName>, domino suo colendissimo.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sangallen.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
